First , mitochondrial volume density is diminished in slow-twitch skeletal muscle of PGC-1  /  mice .
Second , mitochondrial <termsem="GO:0045333"> respiratory </term> capacity is modestly but significantly altered in skeletal muscle and liver of PGC-1  /  mice .
